§ 1673. Repealed. Pub. L. 102–573, title IX, § 901(4), Oct. 29, 1992, 106 Stat. 4591
Section, Pub. L. 94–437, title VIII, § 803, formerly title VII, § 703, Sept. 30, 1976, 90 Stat. 1413; renumbered title VIII, § 803, Pub.
